e操作超时等待\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend服务返回HTTP 500错误，因为checkoutservice的PlaceOrder操作失败，错误传播路径为：shippingservice不可用 → checkoutservice超时 → frontend返回500错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**根因分析总结：**\n\n1. **根本原因**：shippingservice服务完全不可用，IP地址10.233.27.213:50051无法访问\n2. **影响范围**：\n   - 直接受害者：checkoutservice（延迟增加255倍）\n   - 间接受害者：frontend（返回HTTP 500错误）\n3. **错误传播路径**：shippingservice → checkoutservice → frontend\n4. **关键证据**：\n   - checkoutservice调用shippingservice的GetQuote操作延迟从9.3秒增至2385秒\n   - 所有相关调用都返回\"i/o timeout\"和连接超时错误\n   - frontend服务因checkoutservice失败而返回500错误\n\nshippingservice的不可用是此次异常事件的根源，需要检查该服务的部署状态和网络连接。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "shippingservice 服务完全不可用是本次异常事件的根因"}
